Code for SmartyLint was originally was taken from PHP CodeSniffer and modified.

"LICENSE" file (without double quotes) in the distribution maintains copyright notice
of original authors, with additional copyright notice of SmartyLint authors.

Files which are used as it is(with no modification) still have copyright notice of
their original authors. Files which are modified/changed/updated have new authors name
and/or original auhors name. Files which are new have only new authors name.

SmartyLint has nothing to do with "Squiz Pty Ltd" or its contributors.

Thanks to "Squiz Pty Ltd", Greg Sherwood <gsherwood@squiz.net> and
Marc McIntyre <mmcintyre@squiz.net> for creating awesome tool PHP CodeSniffer.
